{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter03_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_2_0",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "",
            "text": "这次大家的矛头都指向了B",
            "portrait": "null",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "这房间里的东西也太可疑了，要我说你就是凶手把",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我之前是设计师，对精巧的东西有浓郁的兴趣，总不能因为这点就断定我是凶手把",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "即使这么说可所有不利的证据还是指向你，光这点你就很难洗脱嫌疑",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "哦？可我觉得酗酒伤人在动机上更合理哦",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "动机...的确作案需要动机，大家昨天跟C在一块儿时干了什么？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "撕...我记得他是说要送我一瓶酒来着？但最后好像不了了之了。",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "晚上C与往常一样来我房间里向我传教，我对他的教义不感兴趣，他自己说完就走了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（说谎）我在白天倒是见过他，口里神神叨叨的晚上喝醉后就不得而知了。",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "总感觉有些话语与之前自相矛盾...",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_ShowChoice_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|line_2_10",
                "B|line_2_21"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不了了之？不不不，证据就是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "没喝过的酒",
                "line_2_11",
                "line_2_18"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_11",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "就是你房间里的那瓶酒，C没有说谎的的确确给你了",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_12",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "可这...又说明什么呢？我咬死是我不记得了你又怎么办？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "嗯？C会无缘无故专门给你送东西吗",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "天底下没有免费的午餐，这不是赠送，而是交换，C与你交换的东西就是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "羊皮纸",
                "line_2_15",
                "line_2_18"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_15",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你床下的羊皮纸，一个酒鬼难道对邪教感兴趣？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "等..等等......",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "胜负已分，你的说辞站不住脚",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "A",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_2_32"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_18",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这点....能证明",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_19",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "果然当初就该把你往死里打！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_20",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "赶紧投票把，浪费时间",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_2_32"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你隐瞒了事实真相，这点就是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "黑皮书",
                "line_2_22",
                "line_2_30"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_22",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你说你一直在看书，那这本与众不同的书该怎么解释",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_23",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我有什么需要解释的？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_24",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你说对宗教无感，为什么还要看这种书？\n而且看位置恐怕是昨天才看，或是昨天某人才给你？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_25",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "呃！！！\n我根本没发现这本书，谁知道C什么时候留下来的",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_26",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，以你的性格不会发这种错误",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_27",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "能证明B强大控制欲望的是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "作息图表",
                "line_2_28",
                "line_2_30"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你强大的控制欲不会允许这种错误\n你并非没理C反而达成了与A和C同样的锲约关系，这样一来，你也有了去C房间的理由",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_29",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "呵呵，确实如你所说，但我去只是寒暄。为了避嫌我只好撒谎说没理C",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "B",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_2_32"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "对！就是这个",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_31",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这根本说明不了任何问题，请你深思熟虑后再发言好吗",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_2_32"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2_32",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "记录完成，下一轮。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_LoadScene_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadScene"
        }
    ]
}